  <strong>Medical Disclaimer</strong><br>
  This article is for educational and informational purposes only. It is not medical advice, and it does not constitute a recommendation for or against any specific product or treatment. The information presented here reflects publicly available research and should not substitute for professional medical guidance. Always consult a qualified healthcare provider before starting, stopping, or modifying any weight management protocol, whether prescription-based or supplement-based. Individual results vary based on genetics, health status, adherence, and many other factors.
</div>

